main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 552/2007 is amended as follows:
1. Annex I is amended as follows:
(a) the amount for the ‘Suckler cow premium’ for Spain is replaced by ‘261 153’;
(b) the amount for the ‘Additional suckler cow premium’ for Spain is replaced by ‘26 000’;
(c) the amount for the ‘Suckler cow premium’ for Portugal is replaced by ‘78 695’;
(d) the amount for the ‘Additional suckler cow premium’ for Portugal is replaced by ‘9 462’;
(e) the amount for ‘Article 69, beef and veal’ for Portugal is replaced by ‘1 681’;
2. Annex II is replaced by the text in the Annex to this Regulation;
3. in Annex III, the amount concerning Portugal is replaced by ‘413 774’.
